defaultBIBLIOGRAPHY
defaultMy name is Nigel Harman and the opinions expressed above are entirely personal.
defaultI have worked in the electrical industry since 1975 as an electrical engineer, college lecturer, 
defaulttrainer and assessor of individuals and inspector of installations
default in electrical installation and renewable technologies.
defaultI am submitting this report because I believe that the electrical industry and it’s
default customers are not being well served by the plethora of qualifications and “schemes” which are simply confusing everybody and having no real impact on unauthorised or sub-standard work.
